{"tid":868183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本天氣女主播是現役大學生 私服照曝光網友全戀愛了！","createTime":"2018-10-19T09:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T09:45:36.000Z","uid":32511,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"97d94eb551763996f73509624496fd69f5d9a55b","tid":868183,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"新聞主播一向給人嚴肅卻不失專業的印象，近日一名氣象女主播「沖田愛加」，掀起日本網友的討論，工作時端莊又專業的她，其實是年僅21歲的大學生，清新脫俗的形象也被網友視為「清純派」主播代表，看了她私服的網友都直呼「反差萌太可愛了」。<br />\n <br />\n根據日本媒體《RocketNews24》報導，21歲的沖田愛加就讀明治大學理工學部，今年4月她開始在富士電視台擔任周六晨間節目的天氣姐姐，負責氣象播報配合節目主題出外景等等，她也時常扮演一日工作系列的角色，因此，長相甜美的她累積了不少粉絲。<br />\n <br />\n而在日本，主播分為「清純派」與「正統派」，沖田愛加被列為「清純派」，網友從她的社群網站上搜出了許多日常照，身為女大生的她穿著清新、活潑，與節目上的端裝樣貌相差甚遠，日本網友也表示「沒想到換件衣服又是不同人的感覺」、「不管哪樣的她都很可愛」、「私底下好像女高中生」、「反差萌是最迷人的」。<br />\n<br />\n日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/172004_550dd024e77dc812452d40d751a2180a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F172004_550dd024e77dc812452d40d751a2180a.png&h=03fdf972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/172302_9bf6ff6cae7c9020b6d31f76490f757e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F172302_9bf6ff6cae7c9020b6d31f76490f757e.png&h=e10c08ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"705385a125a00dfaaf5a95621f14acdd8fba7c67","tid":868183,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac